Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:38.89,Default - 1080,,0,0,0,,Tự nhiên làm sao thế, bà ấy? {What's gotten into you?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:43.99,Default - 1080,,0,0,0,,Tớ không biết! {I don't know!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.73,Default - 1080,,0,0,0,,Sao mà, cứ thấy khác hẳn bình thường. {It's just so different from usual.}
